sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:37:27.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;好多人上街呀&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;廢青嚟嘅&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;唔係喎好多大學生喎&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;嗰班人讀屎片嘅&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;但醫生都反黑警喎&rdquo;<br />\n&ldquo;嗰個醫生實收咗錢啦&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你留意下啲蠢人嘅回應，你會發現佢地講嘅嘢有個特色：無數字性。佢地講嘅嘢唔單只無證據，係直頭你想幫佢搵統計數據嚟支持佢嘅講法都做唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &ldquo;好多人上街&rdquo;係量化到，200萬人，1/4人口，03遊行嘅4倍etc。但&ldquo;廢青&rdquo; 應該點證明？點為之廢？就算你想幫佢搵數據都唔知要搵咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你問多佢幾問，佢就會用&ldquo;總之&rdquo;嚟答你。<br />\n<br />\n我之前試過chok個親戚，我問佢覺得農民起義推翻秦始皇，周朝推翻商紂，係咪為人民做咗好事，佢大大聲答我&ldquo;梗係啦&rdquo;，咁跟住我問佢&ldquo;咁點解學生反呢個無能政府你又覺得唔啱？&rdquo;，佢話&ldquo;因為搞亂個社會&rdquo;，我再問佢咁反秦反商都亂架，打哂仗喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，佢個腦就short circuit咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50b15f3fa83d12a7247ada33406bc488f0e01aa","tid":1262283,"uid":104965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:39:33.000Z","msg":"因為廢老怕無生果金去叫雞"},{"pid":"af046d6c8ecd0f95a5002eb53bf4e654fc46c81f","tid":1262283,"uid":64138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:42:46.000Z","msg":"佢地d分析力去哂d馬同波度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865352e7a8990032f7226fa768fbcd1b49be0369","tid":1262283,"uid":206606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f5d03b75f6934e467fd420b778cea93e1aefd22","tid":1262283,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e6b9b35beb058586b76f84ee1afd4866b00e09b","tid":1262283,"uid":206606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eed646f7653ef4ab2654ce5e7e05d58952ab78c8","tid":1262283,"uid":37389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:10:32.000Z","msg":"簡單啲講：佢地蠢 